{"tid":1613743,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【敵人也在進步】藍絲新職業解鎖：空襲兵","createTime":"2019-10-02T15:21:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T16:19:06.000Z","uid":316410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"89e840b1342908274819e990cd8c178d0849a2a2","tid":1613743,"uid":316410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:21:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫手推<br />\n依家無論你係和定勇<br />\n出去發夢都務必戴上頭盔</span></span><br />\n<br />\n10月1出黃大仙發夢<br />\n同緊黑警對峙個陣<br />\n有好多藍絲在高處攞玻璃樽扔手足<br />\n而被黑警追個陣<br />\n手足們撤退嘅同時 <br />\n亦有唔少既雜物從高處掉落<br />\n砸傷手足<br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係 <br />\n藍絲嘅質素真係好低<br />\n令手足又要防陸地又要防高空<br />\n依家勇定和都好 發夢都有生命危險<br />\n為咗自己 戴個頭盔保護頭部<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"61ae785eee3f4d52a45cd9d5ac035d346cab9c06","tid":1613743,"uid":316410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:56:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f82754059793bea1333381cc97f3c999a977c763","tid":1613743,"uid":316410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:19:06.000Z","msg":"推呀"}]}